      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Squeeze the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lemon quarters </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) into a small bowl</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1578318910279-x200.jpg",
