    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to a large plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Press your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into the<strong> flour</strong>, so they are evenly coated (make sure to shake off any excess!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
