    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the potatoes are fork-tender, add the<strong> spinach</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 1 min or until it's wilted</p><p>Drain everything and return to the pot, then mash together with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic</strong> <strong>mash</strong></p><p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then cover to keep warm until serving</p>",
      "order": 5,
